OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening for Shetland with a few
OL,7,Fshowers, but drier and brighter for
OL,8,FOrkney. The rest of the night will see
OL,9,Ffurther cloud and a few showers.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FA cloudy day with showery
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain, especially for
OL,13,FShetland where rather dull conditions
OL,14,Fwill prevail. Some brighter spells
OL,15,Fpossible for Orkney. Moderate to fresh
OL,16,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
