OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure dominates bringing largely
OL,7,Fsettled but fairly cloudy conditions.
OL,8,FSome bright or sunny spells on Monday
OL,9,Fand Tuesday.
